# LiveGraphPulse - Real-Time Metric Chart

LiveGraphPulse shows your metric streams as smooth, real-time updating line charts.

## Features
- Live scrolling line graph  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Matplotlib rendering  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_LiveGraphPulse.git
cd 32_LiveGraphPulse
python visualize.py
